# Test commands (agents)

On Windows, `vendor\bin\phpunit` has no `.exe` extension. Invoking it directly opens a "choose app" dialog instead of running tests.

**Never** use `vendor/bin/phpunit` or `vendor\bin\phpunit` in shell commands.

**Never** run `docker compose … run composer vue:check` — the `composer` image has no npm. Use `mrt vue-check` or the `vue` service via scripts.

**Prefer** `.\scripts\mrt.ps1` / `bash scripts/mrt.sh` over raw `docker compose` or individual root wrappers — same behaviour, one entry point. See `scripts/README.md` and `docs/DOCKER_SCRIPTS_PLAN.md`.

**Timings:** `-Timings` / `--timings` on gate commands, or `$env:MRT_SCRIPT_TIMINGS=1` / `export MRT_SCRIPT_TIMINGS=1`. Logs `[timing] step — Ns` per major step.

## Unified CLI (`mrt`)

| Context | Command |
|---------|---------|
| Help | `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 help` / `bash scripts/mrt.sh help` |
| Full PHP gate | `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 check` / `bash scripts/mrt.sh check` |
| PHP without PHPCS | `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 check -SkipPhpcs` / `bash scripts/mrt.sh check --skip-phpcs` |
| PHP + Vue | `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 check -Vue` / `bash scripts/mrt.sh check --vue` |
| PHPUnit | `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 test` / `bash scripts/mrt.sh test` |
| Vue | `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 vue-check` / `bash scripts/mrt.sh vue-check` |
| Static E2E (mock) | `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 e2e` / `bash scripts/mrt.sh e2e` |
| WordPress E2E | `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 dev e2e-wp` / `bash scripts/mrt.sh dev e2e-wp` (prepare + restore) |
| Lint | `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 lint` / `bash scripts/mrt.sh lint` |
| Coverage (exploratory) | `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 coverage -Timings` / `bash scripts/mrt.sh coverage --timings` |
| Dev reset | `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 dev reset` / `bash scripts/mrt.sh dev reset` |
| Dev smoke | `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 dev smoke` |
| i18n | `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 i18n` |
| CSV zip | `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 csv zip` |

Root wrappers (`check.ps1`, `test.ps1`, `vue-check.ps1`, `coverage.ps1`, …) still work — use when a doc or habit references them directly.

## Docker dev reset

| Context | Command |
|---------|---------|
| Full reset | `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 dev reset` / `bash scripts/mrt.sh dev reset` |
| Rebuild WordPress image | `-Build` / `--build` |
| Stack already up | `-SkipCompose` / `--skip-compose` |
| Plugin sync (slow Windows bind mount) | `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 dev watch` |

## PHP (root wrappers = same as mrt)

| Context | Command |
|---------|---------|
| Full PHP gate (Windows) | `.\scripts\check.ps1` or `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 check` |
| PHPUnit only | `.\scripts\test.ps1` or `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 test` |
| Single test file | `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 test tests/Unit/SomeTest.php` |
| Host PHP 8.2+ | `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 test -Local` |
| PHPStan + PHPCS only | `.\scripts\lint.ps1` or `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 lint` |

## Vue

| Context | Command |
|---------|---------|
| Full Vue gate | `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 vue-check` / `bash scripts/mrt.sh vue-check` |
| Host Node (optional) | `-Local` / `--local` |

Gates use Docker by default (tools-shell exec, conditional `npm ci`, named volumes). See `docs/PHP_INSTALL_WINDOWS.md`, `docs/DEVELOPER.md`, and `docs/DOCKER_SCRIPTS_PLAN.md`.
